quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  4,34,"Abagabo ni abahagararizi b’abagore kubera bimwe mu byo Allah yarutishije abandi, no ku bw’ibyo batanga mu mitungo yabo. Bityo, abagore batunganye ni abicisha bugufi (bumvira Allah n’abagabo babo), bagacunga neza iby’abo bashakanye mu gihe badahari, kubera ko ari indagizo bahawe na Allah. Kandi ba bagore muzabona ko babigomekaho, mujye mubanza mubagire inama, (nibatisubiraho) mubimuke mu buryamo, (nibinangira) mujye mubakubita (mu buryo bworoheje, niba hari icyo byakemura). Ariko nibisubiraho bakabumvira, ntimuzabashakeho impamvu z’urwitwazo. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Uwikirenga, Usumba byose"
  4,35,"Kandi nimuramuka mutinye amakimbirane aganisha ku butane hagati yabo bombi, muzaboherereze abunzi (babiri), umwe uturutse mu muryango w’umugabo n’undi uturutse mu muryango w’umugore; niba bombi bashaka ubwiyunge, Allah azabibashoboza. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umumenyi uhebuje, Uzi neza ibyo mukora"
  4,36,"Kandi mujye mugaragira Allah, ntimukamubangikanye n’icyo ari cyo cyose; mujye mugirira neza ababyeyi, abo mufitanye isano, impfubyi, abakene, umuturanyi mufitanye isano, umuturanyi usanzwe, inshuti ya hafi, uri ku rugendo n’abacakara banyu. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ntakunda umunyagasuzuguro, umwibone"
  4,37,"Babandi bagira ubugugu bakana- bushishikariza abantu, bagahisha ibyo Allah yabahaye mu ngabire ze. Kandi twateganyirije abahakanyi ibihano bisuzuguza"